&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;Reform Luach is intended to assist Reform rabbis, cantors and prayer leaders in planning worship and synagogue observances.&amp;nbsp; Understanding that every synagogue&#039;s customs are different, Reform Luach offers suggestions for applying Reform siddurim, machzorim, and Torah commentaries to specific days in the Hebrew calendar. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
